.TH manta-cli-console 1  "console " 
.SH NAME
manta\-cli\-console \- Open an interactive console to a node or configuration session
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBmanta\-cli console\fR [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fIsubcommands\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Open an interactive console to a node or configuration session
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
manta\-cli\-console\-node(1)
Connect to a node\*(Aqs serial console
.TP
manta\-cli\-console\-target\-ansible(1)
Connect to the Ansible target container of a configuration session
